eserve">Canvas-based image rendering</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">npm install canvas</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">exceljs</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Export Excel/CSV reports</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">npm install exceljs</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">pdfkit</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">0.15.x</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Export PDF reports</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">npm install pdfkit</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">winston</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Logging</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">npm install winston</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">joi</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">17.x</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Request validation</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">npm install joi</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">prisma</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">ORM (optional but recommended)</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">npm install prisma @prisma/client</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">🤖  GEMINI AI — BIBLE QUESTION GENERATION CRITERIA</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">📅  DAILY QUESTION STRUCTURE (3 Questions Per Day)</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Slot</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Category</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Bible Scope</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Topic Pool</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Difficulty</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Tag Color</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Q1 — Old Testament</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">OT</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Genesis → Malachi</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Events, prophecy, law, wisdom, history, psalms</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">HARD</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">#FF6B35</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Q2 — Gospel</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">NT-Gospel</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Matthew, Mark, Luke, John</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Life of Jesus, parables, miracles, teachings, resurrection</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">MEDIUM</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">#FFC000</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Q3 — Other New Testament</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">NT-Other</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Acts → Revelation (excl. Gospels)</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Paul&apos;s letters, epistles, Acts of Apostles, Revelation</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">#70AD47</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">📝  MCQ STRUCTURE — EACH QUESTION MUST HAVE</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Field Name</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Description</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">question_text</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">The question in Hindi (Devanagari script)</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Mandatory</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">option_a</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">First choice option in Hindi</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">option_b</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Second choice option in Hindi</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">option_c</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Third choice option in Hindi</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">option_d</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Fourth choice option in Hindi</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">correct_answer</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">One of: A, B, C, or D</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">verse_reference</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Bible book + chapter:verse (e.g., उत्पत्ति 1:1)</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">explanation</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Brief explanation of correct answer in Hindi (2-3 lines)</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">difficulty</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">easy / medium / hard</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">category</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">OT / NT-Gospel / NT-Other</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">topic_tag</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">e.g., Creation, Sermon on Mount, Love, Prophecy</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Optional</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">english_question</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">English translation of the question (for admin review)</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">💬  GEMINI PROMPT TEMPLATE</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">You are a Bible quiz expert. Generate exactly 3 Bible multiple-choice questions in Hindi.&#10;&#10;STRICT RULES:&#10;1. Question 1 MUST be from the OLD TESTAMENT (Genesis to Malachi).&#10;2. Question 2 MUST be from the GOSPELS (Matthew, Mark, Luke, or John).&#10;3. Question 3 MUST be from other parts of the NEW TESTAMENT (Acts to Revelation).&#10;4. All text (question + options + explanation) MUST be in Hindi (Devanagari script).&#10;5. Each question must have exactly 4 options (A, B, C, D) with only ONE correct answer.&#10;6. Include the exact Bible verse reference in the format: पुस्तक अध्याय:पद&#10;7. Explanation must be 2-3 sentences maximum.&#10;8. DO NOT repeat questions asked in the last 90 days (context will be provided).&#10;9. Vary topics — do not repeat the same chapter/event consecutively.&#10;10. Return ONLY valid JSON — no markdown, no preamble.&#10;&#10;OUTPUT FORMAT (JSON array of 3 objects):&#10;[&#10;  {&#10;    &quot;slot&quot;: 1,&#10;    &quot;category&quot;: &quot;OT&quot;,&#10;    &quot;question_text&quot;: &quot;...(Hindi)...&quot;,&#10;    &quot;option_a&quot;: &quot;...&quot;, &quot;option_b&quot;: &quot;...&quot;, &quot;option_c&quot;: &quot;...&quot;, &quot;option_d&quot;: &quot;...&quot;,&#10;    &quot;correct_answer&quot;: &quot;A&quot;,&#10;    &quot;verse_reference&quot;: &quot;...&quot;,&#10;    &quot;explanation&quot;: &quot;...(Hindi)...&quot;,&#10;    &quot;difficulty&quot;: &quot;medium&quot;,&#10;    &quot;topic_tag&quot;: &quot;...&quot;&#10;  },&#10;  { ...slot 2 Gospel... },&#10;  { ...slot 3 NT-Other... }&#10;]</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">✅  QUALITY CRITERIA &amp; GUARDRAILS</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Criteria</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Rule</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">100% Hindi in Devanagari script for all user-facing text</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Accuracy</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Every question must be verifiable from the cited Bible verse</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">No Repetition</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Track used questions; Gemini receives last-90-day question IDs to avoid repeats</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Balanced Coverage</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Over a month: cover OT history, OT poetry, OT prophets, all 4 Gospels, Acts, Epistles, Revelation</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Plausible Options</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">All 4 options must be believable — avoid obviously wrong answers</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Verse Accuracy</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Verse reference must exactly match the answer; verify with Bible API before saving</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Difficulty Mix</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Weekly target: 30% Easy, 50% Medium, 20% Hard across all 3 categories</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Explanation</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Explanation must mention the verse and provide context, not just state the answer</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">No Bias</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Avoid questions that favor any specific denomination or interpretation</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Retry Logic</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">If Gemini returns invalid JSON or fails validation, retry up to 3 times before alerting admin</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">🗄️  DATABASE SCHEMA — SUPABASE POSTGRESQL</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">📋  TABLE: USERS</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Column</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Data Type</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">Constraints</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">id</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">UUID</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">PK, auto-generated</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">User unique identifier</t></si><si><t xml:space="preserve">name</t></si><si><